product_name: Open Country Tray for FD-75SK Dehydrator - Set of 2
long_description: Expand the capacity of your Open Country 700-Watt FD-75SK food dehydrator (sold separately) with this set of 2 Open Country trays. Trays are designed so that they don't require any rotation while you're dehydrating your meats, fruits and vegetables. Includes 2 Open Country trays.
